<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 02:32:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军方预计也门战区将变得更加中心化，可能会再次袭击胡塞武装目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-expects-yemen-theater-to-become-more-central-may-strike-houthi-targets-again/00000190-d733-de6f-abb2-dfbfddb80000</link><description>空军的调查发现，空中管制人员发现了在特拉维夫造成一人死亡的无人机六分钟，但由于没有将其视为威胁而没有被击落 ■ 军方加强了防空，特别是在南部地区</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 22:21:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-expects-yemen-theater-to-become-more-central-may-strike-houthi-targets-again/00000190-d733-de6f-abb2-dfbfddb80000</guid></item><item><title>拜登的光荣退出能否将美国从他的宿敌特朗普手中拯救出来？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/will-bidens-honorable-exit-save-america-from-his-nemesis-trump/00000190-d72b-d566-adfa-ff2bd7250000</link><description>经过四个星期无休无止的猜测后，拜登决定退出，这将颠覆 2024 年大选，阻止民主党内爆，并抑制美国盟友的焦虑情绪 — — 当然，以色列除外，其总理是纯正的特朗普主义者</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 21:46:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/will-bidens-honorable-exit-save-america-from-his-nemesis-trump/00000190-d72b-d566-adfa-ff2bd7250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在加沙的家中被狗袭击后，让患有唐氏综合症的巴勒斯坦人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/idf-left-palestinian-with-down-syndrome-to-die-after-dog-attack-in-gaza-home/00000190-d5e5-dbe5-a7fa-f7ff225b0000</link><description>24 岁的穆罕默德·巴尔 (Mohammed Bhar) 在 7 月初的以色列军队袭击中被以色列国防军战犬咬伤，在加沙城的家中死亡。当时他被命令撤离大楼，一周后他的家人发现他死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 21:09:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/idf-left-palestinian-with-down-syndrome-to-die-after-dog-attack-in-gaza-home/00000190-d5e5-dbe5-a7fa-f7ff225b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和美国犹太领导人对拜登退出选举的令人震惊的决定做出反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-leaders-jewish-americans-react-to-biden-decision-to-drop-out-of-election/00000190-d6eb-d566-adfa-ffebebb70000</link><description>宾夕法尼亚州州长乔什·夏皮罗称拜登是“现代历史上最重要的总统之一”，而以色列前总理纳夫塔利·贝内特则称总统是“以色列真正的朋友，在我们最困难的时刻支持我们”</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 21:02:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-leaders-jewish-americans-react-to-biden-decision-to-drop-out-of-election/00000190-d6eb-d566-adfa-ffebebb70000</guid></item><item><title>拜登向以色列提供了关键支持。对许多人来说，他的同理心同样重要</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/biden-offered-israel-critical-support-to-many-his-empathy-was-just-as-important/00000190-d6e4-d566-adfa-ffe6796e0000</link><description>自10月7日哈马斯袭击以来，拜登在几个关键时刻为以色列挺身而出，但他也并非没有红线。以色列政府推卸责任，他拥抱人质家庭</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 20:30:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/biden-offered-israel-critical-support-to-many-his-empathy-was-just-as-important/00000190-d6e4-d566-adfa-ffe6796e0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登支持后，卡马拉·哈里斯在以色列问题上的记录现在受到更密切的审查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/after-bidens-endorsement-kamala-harris-record-on-israel-to-gain-increased-scrutiny/00000190-d69f-d98e-a996-d7bfa7100000</link><description>副总统哈里斯近几个月来被广泛视为拜登政府在以色列问题上的所谓“黑脸”，他在宣布不会寻求连任后不久就得到了拜登的认可</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 19:13:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/after-bidens-endorsement-kamala-harris-record-on-israel-to-gain-increased-scrutiny/00000190-d69f-d98e-a996-d7bfa7100000</guid></item><item><title>新民意调查：70％的以色列人认为内塔尼亚胡在释放人质方面做得不够</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/new-poll-70-percent-of-israelis-think-netanyahu-not-doing-enough-to-get-hostages-released/00000190-d63a-dc1d-a5d1-f73f98ed0000</link><description>随着总理即将启程前往华盛顿，《国土报》独家获得的一项新民意调查显示，只有五分之一的以色列人认为他已经采取了足够的措施来达成释放加沙哈马斯扣押的人质的协议</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 19:11:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/new-poll-70-percent-of-israelis-think-netanyahu-not-doing-enough-to-get-hostages-released/00000190-d63a-dc1d-a5d1-f73f98ed0000</guid></item><item><title>三名民主党人如何为内塔尼亚胡在华盛顿的“全面胜利”铺平道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-21/ty-article/.highlight/how-three-democrats-paved-the-way-for-netanyahus-total-victory-in-washington/00000190-d5c5-d548-a3ba-ffcfbc830000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡本周将庆祝的将是个人和政治上的胜利：10 月 7 日的灾难将永远玷污他的遗产，十个月后，他将在美国之行期间获得新的公众合法性感</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 19:00:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-21/ty-article/.highlight/how-three-democrats-paved-the-way-for-netanyahus-total-victory-in-washington/00000190-d5c5-d548-a3ba-ffcfbc830000</guid></item><item><title>停火。预防加沙和以色列婴儿脊髓灰质炎流行的唯一方法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/cease-fire-the-only-way-to-prevent-polio-epidemic-among-gazan-and-israeli-babies/00000190-d57e-dbe5-a7fa-f77eb5030000</link><description>最近在加沙污水中发现的高传染性脊髓灰质炎病毒的威胁，必须协调和全面地应对。作为以色列公共卫生教授，我们呼吁停火以阻止疫情蔓延</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 17:11:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/cease-fire-the-only-way-to-prevent-polio-epidemic-among-gazan-and-israeli-babies/00000190-d57e-dbe5-a7fa-f77eb5030000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 289 天：以色列称在以色列国防军袭击也门后拦截了胡塞武装导弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-289-israel-says-it-intercepted-houthi-missile-after-idfs-yemen-strike/00000190-d636-dc1d-a5d1-f73f0f2b0000</link><description>以色列荷台达袭击后，胡塞武装称他们向以色列南部埃拉特发射导弹，袭击了红海的美国船只 ■ 以色列称其用“箭 3”防御系统拦截了胡塞武装导弹，中央司令部称其击落了胡塞武装无人机 ■ 犹太定居者袭击巴勒斯坦和以色列团体约旦河西岸的活动分子造成数人受伤 ■ 内塔尼亚胡将于周二会见拜登 ■ 战争进入 289 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 17:10:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-289-israel-says-it-intercepted-houthi-missile-after-idfs-yemen-strike/00000190-d636-dc1d-a5d1-f73f0f2b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将就国际法院裁决将如何影响加沙援助向最高法院提供补充论据</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-give-top-court-supplementary-arguments-on-how-icj-ruling-will-affect-gaza-aid/00000190-d5dd-dac7-a1f8-ddddba5e0000</link><description>法官们正在听取人权组织的请愿书，呼吁增加对加沙的人道主义援助。他们的裁决将影响国家对加沙的责任，国际法院称以色列仍然是占领军</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 16:18:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-give-top-court-supplementary-arguments-on-how-icj-ruling-will-affect-gaza-aid/00000190-d5dd-dac7-a1f8-ddddba5e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对也门的袭击：战术上的成功暴露了战略上的失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-strike-on-yemen-a-tactical-success-that-exposes-a-strategic-failure/00000190-d5c1-dd26-af91-ffffbbe30000</link><description>以色列飞行员飞那么远去轰炸也门的一个港口，这证明了其对伊朗这个真正的、更近的威胁的威慑力是多么有限。责任归咎于总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡，他对伊朗核威胁的痴迷意味着他忽视了其代理人的危险</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 16:17:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-strike-on-yemen-a-tactical-success-that-exposes-a-strategic-failure/00000190-d5c1-dd26-af91-ffffbbe30000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在未咨询总检察长的情况下提交内阁决定，拒绝国际法院的咨询意见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-files-draft-decision-that-rejects-icjs-advisory-opinion-without-consulting-ag/00000190-d544-d65c-a390-fdd598650000</link><description>以色列拒绝国际法院在内塔尼亚胡提交的裁决草案中发表的咨询意见。 “以色列人民不是自己土地和永恒首都耶路撒冷的占领者”</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 13:58:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-files-draft-decision-that-rejects-icjs-advisory-opinion-without-consulting-ag/00000190-d544-d65c-a390-fdd598650000</guid></item><item><title>咨询委员会要求以色列总检察长提供有关本格维尔任命的警察局长腐败指控的详细信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/committee-asks-israels-ag-for-details-on-ben-gvir-picked-police-chiefs-violations/00000190-d4fb-d89a-a1f7-f6fb7b310000</link><description>咨询委员会将于周日就佩莱德的候选资格举行第二次会议，预计将在未来几天内敲定其立场。以色列总检察长尚未就佩莱德的任命给出最终意见，但此前曾表示，委员们应该拥有无瑕疵的记录</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 13:54:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/committee-asks-israels-ag-for-details-on-ben-gvir-picked-police-chiefs-violations/00000190-d4fb-d89a-a1f7-f6fb7b310000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对胡塞武装的袭击：合理吗？是的。比例？不，游戏规则改变者？不太可能</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-attack-on-the-houthis-justified-yes-proportionate-no-game-changer-unlikely/00000190-d52f-d89a-a1f7-f7af04990000</link><description>沙特阿拉伯和阿联酋已经与胡塞武装作战了八年。加沙战争爆发以来，美英已数十次袭击胡塞武装目标。认为以色列的一次袭击就能改变矩阵的想法是错误的。避免多战区冲突的唯一方法是在加沙达成人质和停火协议</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 13:09:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-attack-on-the-houthis-justified-yes-proportionate-no-game-changer-unlikely/00000190-d52f-d89a-a1f7-f7af04990000</guid></item><item><title>弱点：看不到巴勒斯坦人，以色列人就不再看到自己</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-blind-side-not-seeing-the-palestinians-is-not-seeing-ourselves/00000190-d4a6-dd02-a3d3-ffff5e5d0000</link><description>根据当今以色列普遍的情绪，谈论我们在加沙真正所做的事情比在那里实施的实际行为更糟糕</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 10:09:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-blind-side-not-seeing-the-palestinians-is-not-seeing-ourselves/00000190-d4a6-dd02-a3d3-ffff5e5d0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙污水中发现高浓度病毒后，以色列国防军将为以色列士兵接种脊髓灰质炎疫苗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/idf-to-vaccinate-israeli-soldiers-after-polio-found-in-gaza-sewage/00000190-d490-decf-a7b2-d5b797d50000</link><description>根据以色列军队掌握的信息，以色列军队表示，尚未确认加沙有任何临床病例，但确实担心可能爆发脊髓灰质炎，特别是考虑到加沙的情况</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 10:01:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/idf-to-vaccinate-israeli-soldiers-after-polio-found-in-gaza-sewage/00000190-d490-decf-a7b2-d5b797d50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列担心国际法院的裁决将导致国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡和加兰特发出逮捕令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-fears-icj-opinion-will-lead-to-icc-arrest-warrants-for-netanyahu-and-gallant/00000190-d473-dd02-a3d3-ffff9b5a0000</link><description>尽管与国际刑事法院发出国际刑事逮捕令没有直接关系，但法官们将无法忽视国际法院关于以色列违反国际法的咨询意见</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 09:17:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-fears-icj-opinion-will-lead-to-icc-arrest-warrants-for-netanyahu-and-gallant/00000190-d473-dd02-a3d3-ffff9b5a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡“红线”推迟与哈马斯的人质交易，充满希望的布林肯等待以色列总理的“第二天”计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-red-lines-delay-hostage-deal-as-hopeful-blinken-awaits-pms-day-after-plan/00000190-d420-decf-a7b2-d5b751680000</link><description>在总理预计访问华盛顿并向国会发表讲话之前，内塔尼亚胡和以色列谈判团队就人质协议仍存在分歧</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 08:53:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-red-lines-delay-hostage-deal-as-hopeful-blinken-awaits-pms-day-after-plan/00000190-d420-decf-a7b2-d5b751680000</guid></item><item><title>美国：国际法院对约旦河西岸占领的意见可能会使冲突的解决变得复杂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/u-s-icj-opinion-on-west-bank-occupation-could-complicate-resolving-the-conflict/00000190-d3dd-dd02-a3d3-fbdfb0220000</link><description>美国国务院补充说，法院的意见与解决冲突的“既定框架不一致”，华盛顿“强烈反对”各方利用法院的意见“作为进一步单方面行动的借口”</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 06:38:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-21/ty-article/.premium/u-s-icj-opinion-on-west-bank-occupation-could-complicate-resolving-the-conflict/00000190-d3dd-dd02-a3d3-fbdfb0220000</guid></item></channel></rss>